# ============================================================
# Kisan Chat — Local Development
# ============================================================
# API keys are NO LONGER stored here.
# They are kept server-side to prevent exposure in the browser.
#
# For local development:
# 1. Create a .env file at the ROOT of the project (not inside frontend/)
# 2. Add your keys there (see root .env.example)
# 3. Run: vercel dev (from root) instead of npm run dev
# ============================================================
